correctness.rationale: Multiple factual errors, unsupported values, and schema violations are present. Key issues: (1) processParameters.plasmaPower is set to null, violating the schema (should be omitted since SALD was used, not PEALD). (2) processParameters.pressure is incorrect (1 mmHg); the article specifies atmospheric SALD, so pressure should be ~760 mmHg (or clearly indicated as atmospheric). (3) processParameters.flowRates misuse units and data: the numeric values 1.96, 0.25, 0.37 are partial pressures (mbar) reported in the paper, not sccm flows; mapping them to SCM-PER-MIN is incorrect and not traceable. Compounds are also mislabeled (entries for InZnO and InGaZnO instead of per-precursor InOx, GaOx, ZnO). (4) supercycleDesign is invented; the article used coinjection of metal precursors rather than supercycles. (5) thicknessControl inconsistencies: numberofCycles = 1400 paired with filmThickness = 15 nm conflicts with the article (1400 cycles yielded ~250 nm ZnO or ≥60 nm for mixed cases). GPC values for InZnO (1.5 Å) and InGaZnO (1.2 Å) are not reported and likely incorrect; only ZnO GPC ~0.18 nm/cycle (1.8 Å) is supported. (6) materialProperties.opticalProperties fields are set to null, violating schema types; also not reported by the article. (7) materialProperties.electricalProperties.mobility = 3.5 cm2/Vs is a device-level field-effect mobility from TFTs, not an intrinsic film mobility; resistivity and carrier density are null (schema-type violations) and not reported. (8) uniformity (5%), conformality (AR 10), roughness (0.5 nm), and filmDensity (6.0 g/dm3) are not reported anywhere and appear fabricated. (9) deviceProperties: fieldEffectMobility 3.5 cm2/Vs and thresholdVoltage ~ -25 V are supported, but subthresholdSwing (0.5 mV) and onOffRatio (1e6) are not reported and likely incorrect. (10) filmComposition: atomicRatio In:Ga:Zn = 20:8:72 is consistent with the cited TFT example, but elementalConcentration.values = 20% without element context is ambiguous. (11) reactantSelection.purgingGas = Argon is not explicitly stated (SALD eliminates purge steps); carrier gas Argon is correct. (12) aldSystem.reactor.manufacturer = "Not Found" is a placeholder; should be omitted. (13) saturation = True is questionable given the non-ideal, non-self-limiting growth behavior reported for coinjected IGZO. Properties to correct/review: pressure, flowRates (units and mapping), remove supercycleDesign, revise thicknessControl (numberofCycles/filmThickness/GPC) to match text, remove unsupported optical/electrical film properties and nulls, remove unreported uniformity/conformality/roughness/density/SS/onOff values, keep only traceable device metrics (μ_FE, V_th), and adjust purgingGas/saturation to align with SALD as described.

completeness.rationale: The extraction is largely incorrect and incompletely aligned with the article and schema. Key issues: (1) Multiple processes in the article (ZnO, InZnO/IZO, and IGZO depositions) are collapsed into a single process; separate processes should be extracted. (2) Several values are fabricated or not traceable: reactor pressure set to 1 mmHg (article uses spatial atmospheric ALD; only precursor partial pressures in mbar are reported), flowRates entered in sccm using numbers that are actually partial pressures (1.96, 0.25, 0.37 mbar), uniformity (5%), conformality aspect ratio (10), roughness (0.5 nm), film density (6 g/dm3), subthreshold swing (0.5 mV), and on/off ratio (1e6) are not reported. (3) Inconsistencies: numberofCycles=1400 is taken from thickness-vs-cycles experiments, but filmThickness=15 nm corresponds to the TFT sample; these should not be paired. GPC values for InZnO (1.5 Å) and IGZO (1.2 Å) are not provided in the text; only ZnO GPC=0.18 nm/cycle (1.8 Å) is supported. ‘Saturation’=True is not explicitly established for the multicomponent coinjection case. (4) Misrepresentation of process design: a supercycleDesign (1:1:1) is provided, but the article uses coinjection of DEZ, TMIn, and TEGa in the same zone, not supercycles. (5) Schema compliance problems: plasmaPower is set to null (should be omitted or a valid object), opticalProperties fields are set to null (violates schema types), and materialProperties.electricalProperties.mobilty is populated with a device-level field-effect mobility (should instead be under deviceProperties; no Hall data provided). (6) Composition handling: the device composition Ga/(In+Ga+Zn)=8% and In=20% is reported; atomicRatio=“20:8:72” is plausible, but elementalConcentration provides a single 20% value without element labels. Properties to add/review: split into separate processes; correct pressure (atmospheric) and avoid sccm values not reported; remove or justify uniformity/conformality/roughness/density/SS/on-off; relocate mobility to deviceProperties; omit plasmaPower and opticalProperties if not reported; align numberofCycles with the specific sample or remove; remove supercycleDesign or mark not applicable for coinjection; provide composition values with clear element mapping.
